item.title: i rule.
item.description: I got this email on friday: hey, my school says that if we go on nata2.info we will get suspended,why?? hmm. what to think. haha. I laughed and replied that it may be to the innapropriate content that is in the humor section. ;) or maybe I scare them. yea never can tell with schools. check this out - it allows you to “export” your friendster list. heh.
